OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,6,Fsome heavy, spreading east at first.
OL,7,FSoon becoming mostly dry with a few
OL,8,Fshowers. Further rain will spread into
OL,9,Fthe west later in the afternoon.
OL,10,FStrong southerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FEarly showers will clear as
OL,13,Frain in the west, heavy at times,
OL,14,Fspreads steadily east from the
OL,15,Fevening. Drier conditions follow east
OL,16,Ftowards morning. Windy at first.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FDry with bright spells at
OL,19,Ffirst, scattered showers spread east
OL,20,Ffor a time before clearing east
OL,21,Ftowards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
